{"tid":1022594,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"八旬港翁遊高雄意外墮愛河　獲救無恙自行離開","createTime":"2019-02-15T06:33:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-15T06:41:41.000Z","uid":1121,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"084b82591a5ecf52fe745a2eb1664b3f72614e54","tid":1022594,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T06:33:44.000Z","msg":"一名八旬香港籍老翁，周一（11日）晚上在台灣高雄的愛河河邊拍照時，意外墮入愛河，幸及時獲救無恙。<br />\n<br />\n事發於高雄市前金區河東路愛河，消防晚上近9時接報指有人墮河，與警方趕至救起涉事81歲老翁，他獲救後稱拍照時意外失足墮入愛河。救護人員為老翁檢查，發現他無明顯外傷，且意識清醒，毋須就醫，他其後已自行離開。<br />\n<br />\n據台灣交通部觀光局資料，愛河發源於高雄市仁武區，流經高雄市區，為高雄主要河川之一，「猶如城市的母親之河」。<br />\n<br />\n（ETtoday）"},{"pid":"2dc1e673567e355df7ff3fda0c2ec58f02fddf61","tid":1022594,"uid":1121,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T06:34:00.000Z","msg":"墮入愛河<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a3380584e05bddabdfb903f191de491472ca89","tid":1022594,"uid":1713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T06:35:35.000Z","msg":"原來係堅跌落河<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"338c429e8361c874d69432938fa07588f525839f","tid":1022594,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2dc1e673567e355df7ff3fda0c2ec58f02fddf61","tid":1022594,"uid":1121,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T06:34:00.000Z","msg":"墮入愛河<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T06:41:09.000Z","msg":"臨老<del>入花叢</del>墮愛河"},{"pid":"ea4b41a55aded08d5e0e3e787ed73929ad84c3b0","tid":1022594,"uid":31370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"